There aren't any malfunctions anywhere.

22
00:05:04,810 --> 00:05:06,370
Aren't you done fixin' it yet!?

23
00:05:10,810 --> 00:05:14,810
While we're here doin' this, Gohan-chan's
growin' more and more delinquent!

24
00:05:36,840 --> 00:05:38,830
What's the matter, ol' timer?

25
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:42,840
You've got such a serious look on yer mug.

26
00:05:44,510 --> 00:05:46,850
I want to go see Gohan now!

27
