have the ultimate in strength...

35
00:06:34,500 --> 00:06:35,160
Supposin' he does?

36
00:06:35,500 --> 00:06:39,830
As he fights against someone his
equal, Goku just might...

37
00:06:42,840 --> 00:06:46,830
Ah, on the other hand, maybe I'm
worrying unnecessarily.

38
