42
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:23,680
You say I've killed the blameless?

43
00:09:26,790 --> 00:09:31,450
Are you trying to say that what you
Saiyans have done up to now was so right?

44
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:34,110
That's why we were destroyed.

45
00:09:35,790 --> 00:09:37,630
I'm the one who destroyed you.

46
00:09:37,800 --> 00:09:39,790
All of you of monkeys got on my nerves.

47
00:09:42,470 --> 00:09:45,800
And now I'm going to destroy you.

48
00:09:48,810 --> 00:09:50,800
Me, Freeza-sama?

49
00:09:51,140 --> 00:09:56,480
Don't let things go to your head.
There's no way you can win.

50
00:10:01,150 --> 00:10:06,610
Even supposing you were a Super Saiyan.

51
00:10:47,130 --> 00:10:48,790
Father...

52
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:52,780
I ain't forgiving you, even if you apologize.

53
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,110
Dammit!

54
00:15:15,800 --> 00:15:19,070
Y- You dodged it! T- There's no
way you could have!

55
00:16:38,150 --> 00:16:39,810
W- Why you... !

56
00:16:50,830 --> 00:16:54,820
If only I could hit you, you'd be... !

57
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:04,540
Hit me and see.

58
00:17:05,180 --> 00:17:06,840
W- What did you... ?

59
00:17:10,180 --> 00:17:12,170
Mock me, will you!?

60
00:17:27,800 --> 00:17:32,790
You can destroy whole planets, but it seems
you can't even destroy a single man, huh?

61
00:17:33,470 --> 00:17:37,170
W- Wh- What the hell are you!?

62
00:17:38,140 --> 00:17:41,130
As you are surely well aware...

63
00:17:41,810 --> 00:17:46,150
I am the Saiyan who came from
Earth to defeat you.

64
00:17:49,820 --> 00:17:56,160
Despite my calm, quiet heart, I am the legendary
warrior, awakened by intense anger.

65
00:18:11,840 --> 00:18:16,180
I am the Super Saiyan, Son Goku!!

66
00:18:26,120 --> 00:18:29,790
The transcendent power of a Super Saiyan!

67
